snippet.title: CREEK DEVIL:  EP - 73  Amber eyes staring at us.
snippet.description:
Retired Army Colonel recounts his experiences with 
this creature in West Texas including the answer to his question.
A baby gorilla? In Texas?

Bob and Norma from Massachusetts witness notable escalation in Bigfoot 
activity including juveniles watching Bob and Norma as they study the creatures
themselves.  Who is studying who?
